## Title: |cff8B4513Guardian|r|cffffffffHelper|r
## Notes: Guardian Druid Tank Assistant for TBC Classic Anniversary. Rage bar, bear form indicator, Maul queue, auto-attack monitor, buff checker (MotW/Thorns), Faerie Fire & Demo Roar debuff timers, cooldown panel with click-to-cast, and a real-time aggro monitor showing which group members have aggro from how many mobs — with healer highlighting and click-to-target. Fully configurable via right-click on the minimap icon.
## Notes-deDE: Baeren-Druide Tank Assistent fuer TBC Classic Anniversary. Wut-Anzeige, Baerenform-Indikator, Krallenhieb-Queue, Auto-Angriff Monitor, Buff-Checker (MotW/Dornen), Feenfeuer & Entmutigungsgebruell Debuff-Timer, Cooldown-Panel mit Click-to-Cast und ein Echtzeit-Aggro-Monitor fuer Gruppen/Raids. Konfigurierbar per Rechtsklick auf das Minimap-Icon.
